    </span>
  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Crime news: duty rota guidance changes because of COVID-19
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">Deadline for CRM12 duty rota applications is 11 January 2021 with additional guidance to help providers.</p>

  </div>
</div>

<div class="govuk-grid-row">
  <div class="metadata-logo-wrapper">
